Notes: Tournament MVP Taryn Mellody scores 16 points and Casey Thran and Allison
Matt add 12 and 11 points, respectively, as 2nd-ranked Lady Royals defeat
DeSales University, 72-40, to win Freedom Conference championship;
Kirby Lutz leads DeSales with 10 points
Game.Officials: Robin Nagy (R),  Ron Reidinger (U),  Jeff O'Brien (U)
